---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import CTABlock from '../../components/CTABlock.astro';
import RelatedPages from '../../components/RelatedPages.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Insurance, Licensing, and Coverage | Untitled Mixed Media"
  description="General liability insurance, commercial auto coverage, Virginia contractor licensing, and workers compensation. The professional credentials behind every project."
  breadcrumbItems={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'About', url: '/about' },
    { name: 'Insurance & Licensing' },
  ]}
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="pb-0">

    <!-- ─── I · HERO ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Grid: H1 wide, body right-aligned via spacer (no col-start offset) -->
    <section class="pt-36 lg:pt-44 pb-24 lg:pb-32 px-6 lg:px-12 border-b border-slate-gray">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <Breadcrumb items={[
          { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
          { label: 'About', href: '/about' },
          { label: 'Insurance & Licensing' },
        ]} />

        <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-20 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16">
          <div class="lg:col-span-11">
            <h1
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-5xl); line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);"
              data-animate="headline"
            >
              $1M in coverage. Licensed. Insured. Verified before we start.
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 lg:mt-24 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16">
          <div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-5"></div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-10">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
              data-animate="fade"
              data-animate-delay="1"
            >
              Working on your building is a liability decision as much as a creative one. You need to know the person on the scaffolding is insured, licensed, and operating as a real business. Not every muralist or sign painter can say that. We can, and we put it in writing before every project.
            </p>
            <div data-animate="fade" data-animate-delay="2">
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="cta-link group inline-flex items-baseline gap-4 lg:gap-6 font-heading text-titanium-white pb-3 border-b border-titanium-white hover:border-soft-gray"
                style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
              >
                <span>Schedule Your Free Discovery Session</span>
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="cta-arrow inline-block">&rarr;</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── II · THE RISK ────────────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Grid: Split layout. H2 left (col-span-5), body right (col-span-7) -->
    <section class="bg-midnight-graphite py-24 lg:py-36 px-6 lg:px-12 border-b border-slate-gray">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 lg:gap-x-16">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5">
            <h2
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
              data-animate="headline"
            >
              What happens when the painter isn&rsquo;t insured.
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
              data-animate="fade"
            >
              If an uninsured painter falls off a ladder on your property, you absorb the liability. If they damage your building, your tenant&rsquo;s property, or a parked car, there&rsquo;s no policy to respond. If they&rsquo;re unlicensed, the work can void your building&rsquo;s own insurance coverage entirely. These are not edge cases. They are real risks that property managers, commercial landlords, and municipal clients deal with regularly.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
              data-animate="fade"
              data-animate-delay="1"
            >
              You shouldn&rsquo;t have to choose between getting great art and protecting your property. With us, you don&rsquo;t.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── III · WHAT WE CARRY ──────────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Grid: Wide H2, then coverage rows (H3 left col-span-5, body right col-span-7) -->
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-36 px-6 lg:px-12 border-b border-slate-gray">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 mb-16 lg:mb-24">
          <div class="lg:col-span-10">
            <h2
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
              data-animate="headline"
            >
              Full commercial coverage. Certificates provided before work begins.
            </h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- General Liability: featured item with prominent numbers -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-slate-gray" data-animate="fade">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 mb-6 lg:mb-0">
            <h3
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
            >
              General Liability Insurance
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              You&rsquo;re protected against property damage, bodily injury, and issues that arise after the project is complete.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-10 lg:gap-16">
              <div>
                <span
                  class="block font-heading text-titanium-white"
                  style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
                >$500,000</span>
                <span
                  class="block font-mono text-soft-gray mt-2 uppercase"
                  style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xs); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);"
                >per occurrence</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span
                  class="block font-heading text-titanium-white"
                  style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
                >$1,000,000</span>
                <span
                  class="block font-mono text-soft-gray mt-2 uppercase"
                  style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xs); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);"
                >general aggregate</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              If paint damages a surface, if a passerby is injured near the work site, if a completed mural causes an issue after we&rsquo;re done, the policy responds.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Commercial Auto: row with H3 left, body right -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-slate-gray" data-animate="fade">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
            <h3
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
            >
              Commercial Auto Insurance
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              Your property isn&rsquo;t exposed to risk from equipment transport.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              Our vehicle is covered under a commercial policy. Standard personal auto policies exclude commercial use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Workers Comp -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-slate-gray" data-animate="fade">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
            <h3
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
            >
              Workers Compensation
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              You&rsquo;re never liable for on-site accidents.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              Carried when subcontractors are engaged on a project. Required by Virginia law for employers, and required by most commercial property managers regardless.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Virginia Business Registration -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 lg:gap-x-16 py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-b border-slate-gray" data-animate="fade">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
            <h3
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
            >
              Virginia Business Registration
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-4">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              You&rsquo;re working with a legitimate, registered entity.
            </p>
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-base); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
            >
              Untitled Mixed Media LLC is a registered Virginia business. This matters for commercial and government projects where proper registration is a prerequisite.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Certificate guarantee statement -->
        <div class="mt-16 lg:mt-24 max-w-3xl" data-animate="fade">
          <p
            class="pt-8 border-t-2 border-titanium-white font-heading text-titanium-white"
            style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); line-height: 1.3; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
          >
            We provide certificates of insurance naming your entity as additional insured before work begins. No exceptions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ─── IV · PROPERTY MANAGERS ───────────────────────── -->
    <!-- Grid: Split layout. H2 left (col-span-5), body right (col-span-7) -->
    <section class="bg-midnight-graphite py-24 lg:py-36 px-6 lg:px-12 border-b border-slate-gray">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 lg:gap-x-16">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5">
            <h2
              class="font-heading text-titanium-white"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-3xl); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
              data-animate="headline"
            >
              If you manage commercial property, we speak your language.
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-10">
            <p
              class="font-body text-soft-gray"
              style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);"
              data-animate="fade"
            >
              We provide certificates of insurance naming your entity as additional insured. We carry the coverage limits your management company requires. We coordinate access schedules, comply with site safety requirements, and maintain clean work areas. The administrative side of the project is as professional as the creative side.
            </p>
            <div data-animate="fade" data-animate-delay="1">
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="cta-link group inline-flex items-baseline gap-4 lg:gap-6 font-heading text-titanium-white pb-3 border-b border-titanium-white hover:border-soft-gray"
                style="font-size: var(--text-fluid-xl); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);"
              >
                <span>Schedule Your Free Discovery Session</span>
                <span aria-hidden="true" class="cta-arrow inline-block">&rarr;</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <RelatedPages heading="Related" pages={[
      { title: 'Philosophy', href: '/about/philosophy', description: 'Why we start with discovery, not design.' },
      { title: 'Our Process', href: '/about/process', description: 'Three steps. You know what happens at every stage.' },
      { title: 'Murals', href: '/murals', description: 'Hand-painted murals in Richmond, VA.' },
    ]} />

    <CTABlock
      trustLine="Work with a professional who protects your property the same way you do."
    />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* CTA arrow glide */
  .cta-link .cta-arrow {
    transition: transform 360ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }
  .cta-link:hover .cta-arrow,
  .cta-link:focus-visible .cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(0.5rem);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .cta-link .cta-arrow {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
